{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/XcodePreviewSupport","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Architecture and Best Practices","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/ModularArchitecture","doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/SOLIDPrinciples"],"anchor":"Architecture-and-Best-Practices"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/forge\/xcodepreviewsupport"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dependencies that hit the network, access the file system, or perform heavy"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"computation are problematic in Xcode Previews. Forge lets you provide a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"preview"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"factory that is used automatically when running inside a preview — no conditional"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"checks needed in your view code.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"The preview Parameter","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"The-preview-Parameter"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Pass a ","type":"text"},{"code":"preview","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" closure to ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/Container\/provide(_:preview:key:_:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" alongside the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"normal factory:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["public var authService: any AuthServiceProtocol {","    provide(.singleton, preview: { MockAuthService() }) {","        AuthService(network: self.networkClient)","    }","}","","public var networkClient: any NetworkClientProtocol {","    provide(.singleton, preview: { MockNetworkClient() }) {"